\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\sa120\sb120\ltrch\loch {\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::9>[ The scene will end with Evan returning his gaze to Sarah after scanning the room. Normally Sarah would attend such meetings in a business skirt suit, with her hair up in a bun, wearing her glasses. In fact, that is how she was dressed when he saved her from a catastrophic fall on a concrete steps. }
\par\plain {\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 Upon saving her, her glasses fell off and her barrette fell out leaving her long blonde hair cascading to the ground. This led to their first kiss. Today, she was wearing fashionable slacks, and a fashionable button shirt. She wore contacts and set of glasses, and her long wavy blonde hair was cascading down to a length around her shoulder blades.}
\par\plain {\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 Enhance the following paragraph, maintaining a deep POV for Evan. The following scene will be transferring from Evan\loch\af5\hich\af5\dbch\af5\uc1\u8217\'92s thoughts to Sarah's thoughts.]<!$Scr_Cs::9><!$Scr_Ps::7><$Scr_Ps::8>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf6 Gazing at her now, her hair cascading down, free of her typical business persona, she remained as breathtaking to him as the day their eyes first met.  The unforgettable day he saved her from the jaws of concrete steps culminating in an dance-like embrace that led to 'The Kiss'.<!$Scr_Ps::8>}
